   <!-- Allows the FAQ accordians to function on the Bridgeway landing page -->
   <script type="text/javascript">
    jQuery(document).ready(function ($) {
      var $accordian = $('.panel .panel-default');
      var $accordianContent = $('.panel-collapse');
      var $icons = $accordian.find('h3 a');
      $accordian.on('click', function () {
          var $this = $(this);
          var $icon = $this.find('h3 a');
          if ($this.hasClass('active')) {
              $this.removeClass('active');
              $icon.removeClass('icon-minus').addClass('icon-plus');
              $accordianContent.slideUp();
          } else {
              $accordian.removeClass('active');
              $accordianContent.slideUp();
              $icons.not($icon).removeClass('icon-minus').addClass('icon-plus');
              $this.addClass('active');
              $icon.removeClass('icon-plus').addClass('icon-minus');
              $this.find($accordianContent).slideDown();
          }
      });
  });
   </script>

    jQuery(function() {
			jQuery('.navbar .dropdown-toggle').click(function(e) {
				e.stopPropagation(); // stop bootstrap from doing stuff
				e.preventDefault(); // stop link from firing to #
				var n = jQuery('.navbar .dropdown-toggle').index(this) + 1; // which navbar item is this?
              
				// set the dropdown in the #menus to toggled.
				jQuery('#menus .dropdown:nth-child(' + n + ') .dropdown-toggle').dropdown('toggle');
				
				if(e.isPropagationStopped() && jQuery('#menus .dropdown:nth-child(' + n + ')').hasClass('open')) {
					// did all this work? make the li in the navbar set to open for highlighting
					jQuery(this).parent().toggleClass('open');
		      }
				
			});
		});
   </script>
   <script type="text/javascript">
    function WireupSpeedBumps() {
    jQuery('a').filter('[href^=http]').not('.nospeedbump').click(function (e) {
      var r=confirm("You will be leaving mhvfcu.com for a third-party site. We are not responsible for the content on the site and its privacy and security policies may differ from ours. We represent neither you nor the third party in the event that you enter into a transaction.");
      
      e.preventDefault();
      if (r=== true) {
        window.open(jQuery(this).attr('href'),'');
      }
    });
    
    jQuery('a').filter('[href^=mailto]').not('.nospeedbump').click(function (e) {
      var r=confirm("Important! Email transmission is not a secure form of communication. Please do not include any account numbers, social security numbers, or password information in your message.");
      
      e.preventDefault();
      if (r=== true) {
        window.open(jQuery(this).attr('href'),'');
      }
    });
  };
   </script>
   <script type="text/javascript">
    var currentViewMode;
  jQuery(document).ready(function ($) {

   <script type="text/javascript">
    jQuery('#view-mode').click(function(e) {
      setViewPort();
      if (currentViewMode == 'mobile') {
          Cookies.set('view-mode', 'mobile');
      }else{
          Cookies.set('view-mode', 'desktop');
      }
      window.location.href = window.location.pathname;
      return false;
  });
  
  function setViewPort() {
      currentViewMode = Cookies.get('view-mode');
      // set a default cookie if not exists
      if (currentViewMode === '') {
          Cookies.set('view-mode', 'desktop');
          currentViewMode = 'desktop';
      }
    
      if(currentViewMode == 'desktop'){
          jQuery('#viewport-scale').attr('content', 'width=1200');
          jQuery('#view-mode').text('View Mobile')
      }else if (currentViewMode == 'mobile'){
          jQuery('#viewport-scale').attr('content', 'width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0');
          jQuery('#view-mode').text('View Desktop');
      } 
  }
   </script>
